WEBVTT

00:12:55.520 --> 00:13:00.600
We need to make our voices heard
and our dollars count.

00:13:01.400 --> 00:13:06.960
Now, we actually have the ability
to change the world on this one.

00:13:07.640 --> 00:13:10.096
The US and its content,

00:13:10.120 --> 00:13:11.616
films in particular,

00:13:11.640 --> 00:13:16.656
have captured the imaginations
of audiences worldwide.

00:13:16.680 --> 00:13:17.880
Worldwide.

00:13:18.840 --> 00:13:23.216
So that means that the film industry
has unprecedented access

00:13:23.240 --> 00:13:28.256
to be able to distribute
stories about equality

00:13:28.280 --> 00:13:30.496
all around the world.